#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.50"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.50:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.50:0.2"
msgid "5. Rohitassavagga"
msgstr "5. With Rohitassa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.50:0.3"
msgid "50. Upakkilesasutta"
msgstr "50. Corruptions"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.53"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārome, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi "
"upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these four things obscure the sun and moon, so they don’t shine "
"and glow and radiate."

msgctxt "an4.50:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.50:1.3"
msgid ""
"Abbhā, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "Clouds …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:2.1"
msgid ""
"Mahikā, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "Fog …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:3.1"
msgid ""
"Dhūmo rajo, bhikkhave, candimasūriyānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "Smoke …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:4.1"
msgid ""
"Rāhu, bhikkhave, asurindo candimasūriyānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "An eclipse of Rāhu, lord of demons …"

msgctxt "an4.50:4.2"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro candimasūriyānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi "
"upakkiliṭṭhā candimasūriyā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr ""
"These are four things that obscure the sun and moon, so they don’t shine and "
"glow and radiate."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:5.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattārome samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi "
"upakkilesehi upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na "
"virocanti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, these four things corrupt ascetics and brahmins, so they "
"don’t shine and glow and radiate."

msgctxt "an4.50:5.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.50:5.3"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā suraṃ pivanti merayaṃ, surāmerayapānā "
"appaṭiviratā."
msgstr ""
"There are some ascetics and brahmins who drink liquor, not avoiding drinking "
"liquor."

msgctxt "an4.50:5.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "This is the first thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:6.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevanti, "
"methunasmā dhammā appaṭiviratā."
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have sex, not avoiding sex."

msgctxt "an4.50:6.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "This is the second thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:7.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā jātarūparajataṃ sādiyanti, "
"jātarūparajatapaṭiggahaṇā appaṭiviratā."
msgstr ""
"There are some ascetics and brahmins who accept gold and money, not avoiding "
"receiving gold and money."

msgctxt "an4.50:7.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "This is the third thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.54"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:8.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā micchājīvena jīvanti, micchājīvā "
"appaṭiviratā."
msgstr ""
"There are some ascetics and brahmins who make a living the wrong way, not "
"avoiding wrong livelihood."

msgctxt "an4.50:8.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkileso, yena upakkilesena "
"upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocanti."
msgstr "This is the fourth thing that corrupts ascetics and brahmins …"

msgctxt "an4.50:8.3"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ upakkilesā, yehi upakkilesehi "
"upakkiliṭṭhā eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā na tapanti na bhāsanti na virocantīti."
msgstr ""
"These are four things that corrupt ascetics and brahmins, so they don’t "
"shine and glow and radiate."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:9.1"
msgid "Rāgadosaparikkiṭṭhā,"
msgstr "Some ascetics and brahmins"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:9.2"
msgid "eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā;"
msgstr "are plagued by greed and hate;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:9.3"
msgid "Avijjānivutā posā,"
msgstr "men hindered by ignorance,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:9.4"
msgid "piyarūpābhinandino."
msgstr "enjoying things that seem pleasant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.1"
msgid "Suraṃ pivanti merayaṃ,"
msgstr "Drinking liquor,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.2"
msgid "paṭisevanti methunaṃ;"
msgstr "having sex,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.3"
msgid "Rajataṃ jātarūpañca,"
msgstr "accepting money and gold:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.4"
msgid "sādiyanti aviddasū;"
msgstr "they’re ignorant."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.5"
msgid "Micchājīvena jīvanti,"
msgstr "Some ascetics and brahmins"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:10.6"
msgid "eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā."
msgstr "make a living the wrong way."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:11.1"
msgid "Ete upakkilesā vuttā,"
msgstr "These corruptions were spoken of"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:11.2"
msgid "buddhenādiccabandhunā;"
msgstr "by the Buddha, Kinsman of the Sun."

#. <br>
#. VAR: upakkilesehi → upakkiliṭṭhā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.50:11.3"
msgid "Yehi upakkilesehi,"
msgstr "When corrupted by these,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:11.4"
msgid "eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā;"
msgstr "some ascetics and brahmins"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:11.5"
msgid "Na tapanti na bhāsanti,"
msgstr "don’t shine or glow."

#. <br>
#. VAR: asuddhā sarajā magā → addhuvā sarajāpagā (bj) | asuddhā sarajā matā (s1-3) | asuddhā sarajā pabhā (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.50:11.6"
msgid "asuddhā sarajā magā."
msgstr "Impure, dirty creatures,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:12.1"
msgid "Andhakārena onaddhā,"
msgstr "shrouded in darkness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:12.2"
msgid "taṇhādāsā sanettikā;"
msgstr "bondservants of craving, full of attachments,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:12.3"
msgid "Vaḍḍhenti kaṭasiṃ ghoraṃ,"
msgstr "swell the horrors of the charnel-ground,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:12.4"
msgid "ādiyanti punabbhavan”ti."
msgstr "taking up future lives."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.50:12.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.50:12.6"
msgid "Rohitassavaggo pañcamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an4.50:13.1"
msgid "Samādhipañhā dve kodhā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:13.2"
msgid "Rohitassāpare duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:13.3"
msgid "Suvidūravisākhavipallāsā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.50:13.4"
msgid "Upakkilesena te dasāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an4.50:13.5"
msgid "Paṭhamo paṇṇāsako samatto."
msgstr ""
